OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly mist and fog soon
OL,6,Fclearing into a fine, warm day for
OL,7,Fmost with light winds. Cloud in
OL,8,Feastern areas lifting through the
OL,9,Fmorning, leaving plenty of sunny
OL,10,Fspells. The far north and northwest
OL,11,Fwill turn cloudier with patchy rain.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud and light rain move
OL,14,Fslowly across northwest Scotland.
OL,15,FElsewhere mostly clear with light
OL,16,Fwinds, some patchy mist and fog. A
OL,17,Fchilly night with local frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
