OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA chilly start with mist or
OL,6,Ffog quickly dispersing. Most places
OL,7,Fthen warm and sunny with light winds,
OL,8,Fthough northwest Scotland stays
OL,9,Fcloudier, breezier and sees occasional
OL,10,Flight rain.
